#: ../../02-architecture.md:1 848f57fa480b413e9cf47ba029d1487f
msgid "Lazy Todo App — Architecture"
msgstr "Lazy Todo App — 架构"

#: ../../02-architecture.md:5 0a4ed49106c340a2934cb8b9e34dc24d
msgid "C4 Model"
msgstr "C4 模型"

#: ../../02-architecture.md:7 abaf8cf4d94b43fa958d63e788bd206b
msgid "Level 1: System Context"
msgstr "第 1 层：系统上下文"

#: ../../02-architecture.md:9 b00b8f023da2477ab20a27b944580ae5
msgid ""
"Lazy Todo App is a local-first desktop productivity system. It does not "
"depend on any hosted backend. Its only external integrations are "
"operating-system capabilities such as windows, tray menus, notifications,"
" and local file storage."
msgstr ""
"Lazy Todo App 是一个本地优先的桌面效率系统，不依赖任何托管式后端服务。"
"它唯一的外部集成是操作系统能力，例如窗口、托盘菜单、通知以及本地文件存储。"

#: ../../02-architecture.md:23 3a5a953574d746528bda3e8283ae887c
msgid "Level 2: Container"
msgstr "第 2 层：容器"

#: ../../02-architecture.md:25 39d720ed041b42768aba4604e923422a
msgid ""
"The app is packaged as a single desktop binary but runs with multiple "
"cooperating runtime containers inside the Tauri shell."
msgstr "该应用被打包为单个桌面二进制，但在 Tauri 外壳内以多个协作的运行时容器共同工作。"

#: ../../02-architecture.md:50 d48ed66b849e467fb9695901b483201b
msgid ""
"**Boundary rule**: the frontend never talks directly to SQLite or the "
"filesystem. Every state mutation crosses the `invoke()` boundary into "
"Rust first."
msgstr ""
"**边界规则**：前端绝不会直接访问 SQLite 或文件系统。所有状态变更都必须先跨过 "
"`invoke()` 边界进入 Rust。"

#: ../../02-architecture.md:52 383ecf8aba7243a9b6718c84ff11de2d
msgid "Level 3: Component"
msgstr "第 3 层：组件"

#: ../../02-architecture.md:54 37270f27c3e14d08b6b3d12470479a57
msgid "Rust Backend Components"
msgstr "Rust 后端组件"

#: ../../02-architecture.md:92 35aac7aa30da464eb893e514a7466872
msgid "React Frontend Components"
msgstr "React 前端组件"

#: ../../02-architecture.md:132 c4b501115d0b400ab2d8fe113d60dfff
msgid "Level 4: Code"
msgstr "第 4 层：代码"

#: ../../02-architecture.md:134 f0e740b6b681428a99de33bde42bea3c
msgid "Persistence Model"
msgstr "持久化模型"

#: ../../02-architecture.md:136 ee3b0c4cd7ab4333b950152e8abff0b1
msgid "The SQLite schema currently uses five tables:"
msgstr "当前 SQLite 模式使用了五张表："

#: ../../02-architecture.md:138 35f57d33756d44ed8b755cb6335bfaa0
msgid "`todos`"
msgstr "`todos`"

#: ../../02-architecture.md:139 4ebf10d36b184d778cfffc123a04683b
msgid "`sticky_notes`"
msgstr "`sticky_notes`"

#: ../../02-architecture.md:140 194d23404b0a47fd8e1f1803fa4c3c06
msgid "`pomodoro_settings`"
msgstr "`pomodoro_settings`"

#: ../../02-architecture.md:141 ea0096b57a2e48f69f631191d3284ff9
msgid "`pomodoro_sessions`"
msgstr "`pomodoro_sessions`"

#: ../../02-architecture.md:142 4b5c4057f6cf477985f6569093d55c16
msgid "`app_settings`"
msgstr "`app_settings`"

#: ../../02-architecture.md:144 284a3a3a59664fa3a6315f534946efd0
msgid "Two singleton-style tables hold configuration:"
msgstr "其中有两张单例风格的表用于保存配置："

#: ../../02-architecture.md:146 0d50b95949304f438e49a9a491a35e67
msgid "`pomodoro_settings` stores timer lengths plus `milestones_json`"
msgstr "`pomodoro_settings` 保存计时器时长以及 `milestones_json`"

#: ../../02-architecture.md:147 b614c24f0b1242cc8945aceaf3c84b4d
msgid ""
"`app_settings` stores display preferences, note defaults, and storage-"
"related UI hints"
msgstr "`app_settings` 保存显示偏好、便签默认值以及与存储相关的 UI 提示"

#: ../../02-architecture.md:149 48d446b6556549218a524da5c3172b2c
msgid "Representative Flow: Open a Sticky Note in Its Own Window"
msgstr "代表性流程：在独立窗口中打开一张即时贴"

#: ../../02-architecture.md:168 ef8a21bfeb604a2bba3f1bd896576245
msgid "Key Architectural Decisions"
msgstr "关键架构决策"

#: ../../02-architecture.md:151 f13c4f2e46d04c1387b52792d34ddcc6
msgid "Decision"
msgstr "决策"

#: ../../02-architecture.md:151 1785c8a1857a43668d5f5d273033e8d4
msgid "Rationale"
msgstr "原因"

#: ../../02-architecture.md:151 aee7ac1c5c7641c892b78af3b2a27642
msgid "Keep all persistence in `db.rs`"
msgstr "将所有持久化逻辑保留在 `db.rs` 中"

#: ../../02-architecture.md:151 03c73c038ceb4cfeaab354f4fc561874
msgid "Centralizes schema and SQL in one place for a small app"
msgstr "对于体量较小的应用，将 schema 与 SQL 集中在一处更易维护"

#: ../../02-architecture.md:151 42d05cb929f44fc8a9c89948d222985b
msgid "Persist app settings in SQLite"
msgstr "将应用设置持久化到 SQLite"

#: ../../02-architecture.md:151 d2266318509246daa7d269b8a6c92d29
msgid ""
"Settings survive restarts and reuse the same backend contract pattern as "
"other features"
msgstr "这样设置在重启后仍然保留，并且可以复用与其他功能一致的后端契约模式"

#: ../../02-architecture.md:151 19fc272ae8234299870311194b40d513
msgid "Use a separate note window webview"
msgstr "为便签使用独立的 note window webview"

#: ../../02-architecture.md:151 6fc274eae1244f5e9577bc41336f5814
msgid ""
"Gives sticky notes a desktop-native feel without introducing a second "
"frontend bundle"
msgstr "在不引入第二套前端打包产物的前提下，提供更接近原生桌面的即时贴体验"

#: ../../02-architecture.md:151 2e7eabc9a1e9436b88850f8b8b5fd2dc
msgid "Hide the pomodoro tab instead of unmounting it"
msgstr "隐藏番茄钟标签页，而不是卸载它"

#: ../../02-architecture.md:151 a74ac1e3d0e04857889a7dbfc4683adb
msgid "Prevents timer state from resetting when the user changes tabs"
msgstr "防止用户切换标签页时计时器状态被重置"

#: ../../02-architecture.md:151 6c620aca20774df1b53ec4a0e89cf179
msgid "Store pomodoro milestones as JSON in `pomodoro_settings`"
msgstr "将番茄钟里程碑以 JSON 形式存储在 `pomodoro_settings` 中"

#: ../../02-architecture.md:151 28f8c82002904fb293db5c0e5b1fc4c5
msgid ""
"Keeps milestone data attached to the singleton timer config without "
"another relational table"
msgstr "无需增加新的关系表，就能让里程碑数据与单例计时器配置保持绑定"

#: ../../02-architecture.md:151 c8d5459e728a476eb974198bd2546b92
msgid "Resolve DB location from env, then config file, then app data"
msgstr "数据库路径按 env、配置文件、应用数据目录的顺序解析"

#: ../../02-architecture.md:151 eb8a4912f1934340a4478072b475294c
msgid "Supports both ad hoc overrides and persistent local configuration"
msgstr "同时支持临时覆盖和持久化本地配置"

#: ../../02-architecture.md:151 9ed47732826940549802ff9a58df6863
msgid "Open external links with the shell plugin"
msgstr "使用 shell 插件打开外部链接"

#: ../../02-architecture.md:151 112e4618c1894be0924ab95781368deb
msgid ""
"Avoids in-webview navigation and keeps Markdown note links safe and "
"predictable"
msgstr "避免在 webview 内部跳转，使 Markdown 便签中的链接行为更安全、可预期"

